        <num>CC 782</num>
        <heading>782.  Abandonment of plan or of restriction</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 782.  Abandonment of plan or of restriction.
Building restrictions terminate by abandonment of the whole plan or by a general abandonment of a particular restriction.  When the entire plan is abandoned the affected area is freed of all restrictions; when a particular restriction is abandoned, the affected area is freed of that restriction only.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
